author: Andrea Park CBS News
title: Jessa (Duggar) Seewald shares pregnancy video
text:
This baby is going to be one very energetic bundle of joy.
Reality star Jessa (Duggar) Seewald showed off her pregnant belly on Instagram as it squirmed and shook.
"So weird and yet amazing to see my baby move like this! Finally managed to capture one of those super active moments," wrote Seewald. " I know, I'm a bit obsessed ... but this Mama is absolutely fascinated! Here's what the #BabyBump looks like from my perspective."
Seewald has not revealed the baby's gender and hinted before that she may be pregnant with twins; however, she referred to a "baby" in her post instead of "babies," so perhaps she's only due to have one. It will be the first child for Seewald and her husband Ben.
Though the Duggar family has been rocked by Josh Duggar's scandals , Seewald seems to be keeping her head up by posting about her pregnancy and spending time with her nieces and nephews.
TLC will air a special on Seewald's pregnancy.
